parameters:
\ncAh, thank you, Kei-chan. Thank you so much. I will never
forget this favor...

\nc<>It's too early to express gratitude. Let's escape quickly
before the enemy returns.
\nc<Bad Uncle>Oh, I won't let you do that!

\ncFrom the looks of it, it seems like that girl over there
caused trouble. How dare they embarrass me like this.
\nc<Bad Uncle>Don't think you can get away with this for free.
\nc<>(Gun!! Why is that person... Damn it...!)
\nc<Bad Uncle>Oh, it's better if you don't move.

\ncThe moment you do something, whether it's an act of
hostility or not, I will shoot you immediately.
\nc<Bad Uncle>This is not a threat, it's a report.

\nc<>(What should I do? If I transform into a magical girl, I can
protect myself, but...) (My true identity will be
exposed...)

\nc<>(No, this is not the time to be dawdling. I have to do it
now before it becomes irreversible!)
\nc<>My my, you've really done it, haven't you?

\ncThe founder of the Rakuen religion!! Finally, they make an
appearance.

\nc<>Yes, I hurried back because it seems like troublesome people
have arrived.

\nc<>Geez, we're busy dealing with magical girl countermeasures
over here.

\ncComing here alone and doing something incomprehensible
again. You really have no regard for your life, huh?

\ncWell, fine. If we just kill this one, it'll be over. You
guys, shoot--
\nc<>Do you not even know what you picked a fight with?

\nc<>Let's make up for your ignorance and sins by supporting the
paradise of our religion.
\nc<>Kyaa, Founder-sama? What on earth is that appearance...

\ncAnswer, Founder! Lately, you've been engrossed in something
without telling us.

\ncI believed in you and waited because it was you, but now
that it has come to this, I can't stay silent--.

\nc<>Hmm, by the time you wake up, you will have forgotten
everything. It's a little bit regretful.
\nc<>Let's move everyone so that the ordinary believers can rest.

\nc<>...Cashew Nut, did you see!? Villan was pretending to be the
founder!

\nc<>No, that's not it. Even when in human form, you should be
able to sense the aura of the other world, nya!
\nc<>\c[2]I became Villan while still being human, nya!\c[0]

\nc<>No way. If they were able to, it would have been a major
problem caused by the villains who infiltrated human
society, nya.

\nc<>This is an exception within an exception. So, is there a
possibility that the other villains in this town are human?
\nc<>Alright. Let's escape from here for now and think.

\nc<>I obtained the memory N4: The True Identity of the
Founder.
